{"tid":49473,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"女裝錶求推介","createTime":"2016-12-21T17:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T14:10:01.000Z","uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b2b09890725cff544c5865a1948e2e8a88977fc","tid":49473,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:27:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的,<br />\n黎緊想送隻錶俾女朋友,見佢戴嗰隻三百零蚊既casio都殘殘地,但我又無戴開錶,所以想係到問下大家.<br />\n1000蚊以下既筆直,無牌子要求.可唔可以推介啲錶款俾小弟參考下.希望係皮帶錶,白色錶面(黑色都可以接受),雖然係女裝錶,但錶面想大小小(同普通男裝錶差唔多大細)<br />\n我同女朋友仲係學生,所以無咁多錢,請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登有愛,無言感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4eeaa82e2257c210a7f512e2b757a8f9b28f88","tid":49473,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc2ec2f77486d4cb50f2b462b3b7bd1ab4ec4336","tid":49473,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3326f4aa24e6b597a02f5bbad3e9a2d8f477974","tid":49473,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:42:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;</strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f332514fd66c5564e78b78683fe63de32508f10","tid":49473,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:48:52.000Z","msg":"豬叔"},{"pid":"30ed6bb35666ff18ec066552b85ca37379ecccd0","tid":49473,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豬叔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢中意皮帶多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedbac0aabe4de6edd2696f80fafb03fa571d911","tid":49473,